晚上（8 月 16 日），斯威夫特表演了另一场“Eras”巡演首秀“London Boy”。摘自她2019年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-lover-review-2541084">Lover</a> 》。斯威夫特在介绍这首歌时说道：“整个晚上我都在想‘上帝，我爱英国人。’”</p><p>这是她自 2019 年发行这首以首都为灵感的歌曲以来首次现场演奏。为了纪念这一时刻，她还修改了歌词，加入了“我喜欢在温布利打球”这句话。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784573" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784573" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784573" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="8 月 16 日，泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在温布利球场 (Wembley Stadium) 比赛。图片来源：TAS2024/Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-playing-Wembley-Stadium-on-August-16.-Credit_-TAS2024_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784573" class="wp-caption-text"> 8 月 16 日，泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在温布利球场 (Wembley Stadium) 比赛。图片来源：TAS2024/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>伦敦演出标志着斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-cancels-vienna-eras-shows-following-planned-terror-plot-3781881">在维也纳的三场演出</a>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyer-for-suspect-in-taylor-swift-vienna-terror-plot-says-accusations-are-exaggerated-3783655">恐怖袭击阴谋被挫败而</a>被取消以来的首场“Eras”音乐会。事件发生后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-changes-wembley-stage-times-following-foiled-vienna-terror-plot-3783073">，斯威夫特最近在伦敦的舞台时间不得不进行调整</a>。温布利大球场还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tay-gating-wembley-stadium-issues-statement-to-taylor-swift-fans-hoping-to-gather-outside-venue-3783014">发表声明，警告无票球迷在音乐会举行期间不能站在场外</a>，这种趋势被称为“泰式门控”。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-edinburgh-3763814?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAR3aUrwDuJgnDfhL31UDsmnsruamExATeZ01eTeIL676mvOLqfs_qSqlcDA_aem_AdsNpowi-Oeil7ifBwJkCYIrutAyvrSApL7euoOaAMY46dLmNBFUoLD_G-AIDSNpm0UoyBr960w58VftuHOrt-ne">在爱丁堡举行的英国“Eras Tour”揭幕战</a>的五星级评论中写道：“尽管这是一场舞台表演，但在一个巨大、洞穴般的场地中，斯威夫特和她的歌迷们成功地建立了一个社区。</p><p> “陌生人交换友谊手镯，一起欢笑，一起哭泣，拥抱巡演中的笑话和传说（例如在‘精致’期间大喊‘一、二、三，让我们去吧’）。这就是斯威夫特的力量，这位艺术家<a href="https://news.stv.tv/north/loch-tay-renamed-in-honour-of-taylor-swift-ahead-of-sold-out-murrayfield-concerts-in-edinburgh">不仅激发了苏格兰湖的重新命名</a>，还激发了无数粉丝站出来拥抱成为 Eras 家族的一员。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784375" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784375" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784375" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Vittorio-Zunino-Celotto_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Vittorio-Zunino-Celotto_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Vittorio-Zunino-Celotto_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management--400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Vittorio-Zunino-Celotto_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management--800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/